{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9835dd17a6","title":"大字报摘录","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d0136b510e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"9835dd17a6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4e38dc5cec","name":"西北师范学院"},{"id":"5378a8871a","name":"学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7a2ef2c6a0","type":"title","text":"大字报摘录","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"83d9deed3f","type":"authors","text":"西北师范学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"f5b48ff66e","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“打倒一党专政，实行民主办校！”——地雷","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"dc2df01910","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“打碎枷锁，争取自由！”——无名","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"312432c5b7","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“打倒新党棍，争取自由”——未署名","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"a6c689a239","type":"paragraph","text":"4．“党委领导已造成恶果累累，我们要求取消这种必然独裁……”——被统治者们","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"b0abf66816","type":"paragraph","text":"5．“保民而王”莫之能御也。共产党是一党专政，莫之能御也。足见现在比过去进步。党中央曰：联系群众是党的生命，地方党委是官僚主义，宗派主义是党的生命，足见地方比中央实际。“——动起来","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"7e9b9d4e4c","type":"paragraph","text":"6．……民主与共和的胜利果实，被共产党的宗派主义者们一口吞光了。……”——A、B、C","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"4ed55d0fbc","type":"paragraph","text":"7．“我们要充分的民主，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"ef592c236b","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要自由的呼吸。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"c443e43b67","type":"paragraph","text":"宗派主义毒化了我们的空气","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"40772d7313","type":"paragraph","text":"便衣警察把我们的呼吸窒息。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"b13b0e7ed6","type":"subtitle","text":"我们要打倒宗派主义的党棍，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"ab20575d79","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要反对便衣警察的监视。”——投枪","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"9cac7c954b","type":"paragraph","text":"8．“学校的大小工作总要安插一个党员来领导，甚至一些不称职的党员也要党提上台来担任，试问宗派主义还能严重到什么程度？”——快中子(化)","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"d8cae684ed","type":"paragraph","text":"9．“我院党的领导和行政领导，从来都是一个鼻孔出气的，民主自由统统被他们扼杀了，自上而下的形成了一个魔鬼集团，一贯压制言论自由，……”——(数二r)","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"4a88cf6a84","type":"paragraph","text":"10．昏王昏王，纵使豺狼，学校变成兵营，谁敢与它违抗，豺狼呀，豺狼，更加疯狂，咬伤人命，并不赔赏。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"11e3dd85d1","type":"paragraph","text":"昏王昏王，鼻孔朝上，赦去兰花，弃了麝香，臭花毒草，充满一堂，昏王昏王，庶民遭殃。(落后社)","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"da7436cebf","type":"paragraph","text":"11．党棍们！过去如狼如虎咬群众，现在如虫如鼠藏屁股。(X光)","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"306991d937","type":"paragraph","text":"12．我们每个宿舍里住下一个便衣警察(党员)二个兵卒(团员)监视同学们的一举一动，使大家失去了人身不可侵犯的权利——民主权、幸福权、自由权。(落后社)","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"7854ca558f","type":"paragraph","text":"13．院领导——“奴隶主”……高高在上的老爷们，赶快放下专凭政治资本(党员)作威作福的臭架子，收起你们锦囊中镇压群众的法宝——政治大帽子、禁口壶、长枪短剑……，变“屠杀场”(西北师范学院)成为名符其实的培养社会主义文教干部的园地。(数、和风)","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"9fc4dbb6c5","type":"paragraph","text":"14．入党条件、师院奇闻","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"f14d1b736d","type":"paragraph","text":"奇怪奇怪真奇怪，党门专为少女开。——和尚不平","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"16b5322325","type":"paragraph","text":"奇怪奇怪真奇怪，马屁一拍党门开。——不平者","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"ae85071835","type":"paragraph","text":"15．万古奇冤，枉死孤魂，徒叹息，目者痛。——伸张正义者","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"d651eac80b","type":"paragraph","text":"16．过去我院由于李坤专政，形成大的专政集团，暗无天日，私立牢房，剥夺了许多老师的自由和民主，造成红色恐怖，违反中华人民共和国宪法，……我们要坚决打倒李坤——马步芳二世，——高压电","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"b3227b36e1","type":"paragraph","text":"17．李坤的错误，实际上就是党的错误。——蒺藜社","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"df96d58a91","type":"paragraph","text":"18．“血债要用血来还！以命赏命！”——前哨——","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"74739eea55","type":"paragraph","text":"19．“我们要为受屈的老教授伸冤，为死难的同学报仇，不杀李坤死不冥目，誓不甘休，袒护李坤的走狗滚出去！”——了众","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"f59a8fa8ad","type":"appellation","text":"20．“肃反错害了好多人，眼泪成渠血斑斑”——氢气弹","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"124c1cdf1c","type":"paragraph","text":"21．六月十八日学委会布告张贴出来后，一位同学说：“雷诺杀死中国人刘自然逃到美国，李坤杀死了六条人命逍遥兽医学院，这还是人权吗？”","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"deecfea239","type":"paragraph","text":"22．学生宿舍楼北边厕所的西墙上写着一句话，“西北师范学院是智的监狱。”——署名：反革命分子。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"},{"id":"aa7eb604da","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《香花乎？毒草乎？(2)》（西北师范学院反右斗争委员会，1957年7月6日）。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6"}],"page":{"id":"19c6413dd9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9835dd17a6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}